<item>
            <title>[HBASE-6112] Fix hadoop-2.0 build</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/HBASE-6112</link>
                <project id="12310753" key="HBASE">HBase</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Some of the pom definitions are broken for the Hadoop 2.0 build. Its breaking the build for that version&lt;/p&gt;</description>
